{"tid":2065832,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"利物浦或需移師到停車場慶祝聯賽封王","createTime":"2020-06-16T00:34:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T07:39:37.000Z","uid":28435,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"2e9103a7844b464b333894b8a77b4ec74c257df3","tid":2065832,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T00:34:52.000Z","msg":"在聯賽榜以25分領先的利物浦下周日會作客愛華頓，進行復賽後首場比賽，一旦位列次席的曼城在周三不敵阿仙奴，利物浦如能在這場默西賽德打吡戰贏波，即可奪得30年來首個頂級聯賽冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n英國傳媒報道，由於英超指引需要保持社交距離，愛華頓計劃在葛迪遜公園球場的停車場搭建兩個臨時更衣室予利物浦使用，一個予球員使用，另一個讓職員使用，故他們將不能在同一個房間內慶祝。"},{"pid":"62b1462f45e0f76dffd8c737b5228c2d4bfd2dad","tid":2065832,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T00:51:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85886f66bda9920f713cd60fda62023db461b580","tid":2065832,"uid":2419,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T00:54:41.000Z","msg":"一旦位列次席的曼城在周三不敵阿仙奴<br />\n<br />\n即係唔會發生"},{"pid":"51af966530ab1bc58459fbb4687c5192f291f1f2","tid":2065832,"uid":28155,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T00:55:23.000Z","msg":"愛字頭會唔會搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a88d4b557fd127ee583aa85563e6c457ce4c0f09","tid":2065832,"uid":47268,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T00:58:07.000Z","msg":"我係愛狗就過去搞串個場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaa2edca71a1bc4806985e205a37971686434b52","tid":2065832,"uid":12034,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T01:00:03.000Z","msg":"不如整間房比利記6個6個咁入去輪住慶祝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"283e2bdf15ded680473b5df3345bff02c72a8137","tid":2065832,"uid":99973,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T01:03:22.000Z","msg":"拎冠軍都柒撚過人<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm